Objective: Enforce integrity and safety constraints.
Missing/Empty Sections
Flag and report with section name and position
Short Sections (<50 words)
Flag and suggest fallback strategy (e.g., merge with adjacent section)
Hallucination Mitigation
Cross-check summaries against original section text
Disallow speculative or inferred claims
Long-Paper Chunking
Apply PS2 context-window strategies:
Chunk sections exceeding context limits
Maintain semantic continuity across chunks
